  <title>ASP Glimpse Module</title>
  <description />
  <content>&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Now there’s a pretty sweet way of looking at what’s happening on your server, I’ve picked this tip up from watching SHanselmans MS Stack Of Love (recommended watch) @ MIX11 this year.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Here’s how, (pardon the screenshot file sizes as usual ..)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;1) Create an application&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_42.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_thumb_42.png" width="425" height="385" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;2) Add a package&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_43.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_thumb_43.png" width="244" height="129" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;3) Search online for glimpse and install&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_44.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_thumb_44.png" width="538" height="357" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;4) Add at least one Trace to demo an additional Glimpse feature&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_45.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_thumb_45.png" width="511" height="133" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;5) Fire up your app and go to &amp;lt;appurl&amp;gt;/Glimpse/Config, and Turn Glimpse On&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_46.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_thumb_46.png" width="645" height="528" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;6) Click on the beady little eye on the bottom right corner of your webpage&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_47.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_thumb_47.png" width="562" height="332" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;7) Voilá&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_48.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="/blog/image.axd?picture=image_thumb_48.png" width="745" height="473" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
